     ___                &kp TAB            &hml LALT LC(BSPC) &hml LCTRL BSPC    &hml LSHFT ENTER   ___                    &kp LEFT           &hmr RSHFT DOWN    &hmr RCTRL UP      &hmr RALT RIGHT    ___                ___
